title: Essential Dog Care
description:
Product Description
This "How To" for dog owners explains in a quick, fun, and easy way, 3 procedures Veterinarians want dog owners to know. Learn the right way to clip your dog&#039;s nails, brush your dog&#039;s teeth, and clean your dog&#039;s ears for a happier and healthier pet. Produced by Dr. Lara Nicolayevsky and Dr. Lisa Silberstein of Vet Teach. 

Review:
As a private practice veterinarian and pet owner, I have been waiting a long time for a product like this. The images and instructions are entertaining and easy to understand. The DVD has been really well received by my clients and I even use it to help teach my new technicians. Thank you Drs. Lisa and Lara!
